name: Hawker Center for Integrative Medicine - COVID Vaccine Clinic
notes:
At the Hawker Center, we provide a warm oasis of peace and comfort, treating our patients and their stories with patience and respect. Imagine a spa-like atmosphere where a highly-trained doctor or nurse is administrating the COVID19 vaccination. That’s the Hawker Center difference.
***We currently are providing the 1st and 2nd doses of MODERNA.*** Please sign up for an appointment time.  Please arrive no more than 10 minutes prior to your appointment time. Expect to stay for 15 minutes after you receive your vaccine to monitor for any adverse reaction.***If you would like to find out more information about our clinic, please visit our website at www.hawkerhealth.com***
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Yakima County Health District COVID Vaccination Site
notes: ***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!! The vaccination clinic will take place in the gymnasium of Lewis and Clark Middle School. Masks are required. Please wear clothing which allows access to your shoulder. Vaccinations at this site are reserved for people who live and/or work in Washington State. All individuals 12 and over are eligible to get vaccinated. Those under 18 must be accompanied by a parent/guardian or must get parental consent via video/phone call or paper format. La clínica de vacunación se ubicara en el gimnasio de la escuela intermedia Lewis and Clark. Se requieren máscaras. Por favor, use ropa que permita acceso a su brazo. Las vacunas en este sitio están reservadas para las personas que viven o trabajan en el estado de Washington. Todas las personas mayores de 12 años son elegibles para vacunarse. Los menores de 18 años deben estar acompañados por un padre/tutor o deben obtener el consentimiento de los padres por video/llamada telefónica o en papel. ***1ST & 2nd DOSE PFIZER VACCINATIONS!!!!***!!!!VACUNAS DE PRIMERA Y SEGUNDA DOSIS PFIZER!!!
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

name: Community Vaccination Center at Bellingham Technical College
notes:
College Days One and Done (Janssen) Clinic!  Be prepared for the fall semester vaccination requirement with a single vaccination visit.  All adults 18 and over are welcome to register and attend - first come first served.  Walk-ins are welcome.

If you are having difficulty signing up via the web-site, or need additional assistance, please call our Vaccine Access Scheduler Line at 360-778-6075 on Monday through Friday from 8:30 AM to 4:00 PM.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

notes:
Mobile Vaccine Clinic at North Fork Brewery. Walk-ins welcomed. 
After your vaccination, enjoy an on-the-house draft beer or root beer at the brewery! 
Vaccine is free and will also enter you into the
Washington State Lottery "Shot of a Lifetime" Million Dollar Drawing!
Offering Moderna first or second doses.  Bring your card for second doses.
If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.
